Package: json64
Type: Package
Title: A base64 encode/decode package with support for JSON output/input and UTF-8
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Mauricio Santelices
Maintainer: Mauricio Santelices <m.santelicesa@gmail.com>
Description: The package contains three functions: j_encode and j_decode. The first function let you transform a data.frame or list to a base64 encoded JSON (or JSON string).    The j_decode function takes a base64 string (could be an encoded JSON) and transform it to a data.frame (or list, depending of the JSON structure).    The j_save function is intended to save an encoded output as a .txt file.
